eph Henry statue marker|work=[http://www.hmdb.org/results.asp?SeriesID=17 Markers Attached to Sculpture series]|publisher=[http://www.hmdb.org/ HMdb.org: The Historical Marker Database]|accessdate=2010-10-27}}</ref><br />
Smithsonian Carousel<ref name="Smithsonian carousel">(1) {{cite web|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/6738HLmWZ|archivedate=2012-04-19|url=http://nationalcarousel.org/cgi-bin/census/census.pl?NCANo=39|title=Smithsonian Carousel: The National Mall: Washington, D.C.|publisher=[http://nationalcarousel.org/ National Carousel Association]|accessdate=2012-04-19}}<br>(2) {{cite web|last=Benson|first=Chris|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/6737iLcca|archivedate=2012-04-19|url=http://www.nca-usa.org/psp/NationalMall/#|title=The NCA Photo Show Project Presents: The 1947 Allan Herschell Carousel at The National Mall, Washington, DC|accessdate=2012-04-19|publisher=[http://nationalcarousel.org/ National Carousel Association]}}</ref><ref name=nathan>Nathan, Amy. Round and Round Together: Taking a Merry-Go-Round Ride into the Civil Rights Movement. Philadelphia: Paul Dry Books, 2011. pp. 3, 15-19, 220-224</ref><br>
|}

